ind":"text","text":": (T, Msb:) one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musoEadN","text_ar":"مُسْعَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) fem. of the former [and latter] with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEadaA='u","text_ar":"سُعَدَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, TA,) and, accord. to Lh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEiyduwna","text_ar":"سَعِيدُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asaAEidu","text_ar":"اَسَاعِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but ISd says, I know not whether he mean [of] the [proper] name or of the epithet; but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asaAEidu","text_ar":"اَسَاعِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEiydN","text_ar":"سَعِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is anomalous: (TA:) the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoEuwdN","text_ar":"مَسْعُودٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoEuwduwna","text_ar":"مَسْعُودُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masaAEiydu","text_ar":"مَسَاعِيدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahor","text_ar":"نَهْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"river,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rivulet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"canal of running water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that irrigates the land in the parts adjacent to it, when it is appropriated thereto:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahor","text_ar":"نَهْر"},{"kind":"text","text":": the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahor","text_ar":"نَهْر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for irrigation"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a tract of seed-produce: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suEudN","text_ar":"سُعُدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","T","K","TA","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}